      "left against medical advice (LAMA) Acuity-only baseline     0.0346                       0.0464   0.6244              1.344              0.0000                 0.0575                  0.0594               0.1718                    0.0594            1.718            \n",
      "left against medical advice (LAMA)             lightgbm     0.0346                       0.0444   0.5978              1.283             -0.0021                 0.0512                  0.0469               0.1356                    0.0469            1.356   NO_SIGNAL\n",
